								<wikidot:authorUserId>4980602</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I love the sense of mystery underneath the carefree charm that is skillfully built up throughout. You just <em>know</em> something is off and you're trying to figure out what the anomaly here is, with small hints dropped here and there.</p> <p>I'm confused by the end though. The memetic effect doesn't seem to translate to pictures, so WWS and now the adoption agency are both cognizant of it, right?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
