					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So after <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span> did his Adoption Poster, I just had to try my hand at it, and I had been wondering what would happen if Wilsons got their hands on <span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span></span> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1152">SCP-1152</a>.</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" >Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2425082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="DrAnnoyingDog" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2425082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" >DrAnnoyingDog</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmacro" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3296783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="DrMacro" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3296783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmacro" >DrMacro</a></span>, who gets an EXTRA thanks for helping me come up with a better twist.</p> <p>EDIT-<br /> image attribution is <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Curious_Raccoon.jpg">here</a> and is CC 3.0.<br /> Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2375337&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1569428164" alt="C-Dives" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2375337)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" >C-Dives</a></span> I have a new image for Bandit's true form! Its CC BY SA 2.0 and can be found <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/weasello/344738121/">here</a>!</p> 
